column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, up_sep) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, up_sep) IS NOT # SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camCol, p.field, p.obj, IS# (s.plate, #) as plate, IS# (s.mjd, #) as mjd, IS# (s.fiberid, #) as fiberid FROM ..Star AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id ORDER BY x.up_id
